Check example.test for how to set up a test file. Tests are then run with

./runTests.py example.test

where the input file of course can be something other than "example.test".



check energy and forces:
loose:      energy (1-5)  force (5e-2)
good:       energy (1-7)  force (5e-3)
tight:      energy (1-9)  force (5e-4)
verytight:  energy (1-11) force (5e-5)
